Create a WS and Connect to GIT
-------------------------------

Create a Project in IDE & Create a corresponding empty Repo in GIT
Go to IDE Terminal & Execute -
  - git init
  - git status                              // list the files to Commit
  - git add .                               // All files
  - git commit -m "<Comment>"
  - git remote add origin <URL of Repo.git> // Synch with GIT
  - git push -u origin master               // Push into Repo, master is the new branch
  
 CTRL + K                                   // Commit All in IntelliJ
